snippet.title: We Are Extremely Sad To Report About Sad Ending of Lynda Carter After 'Wonder Woman'
snippet.description:
Lynda Jean Cordova Carter is an American actress, singer, and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Miss World USA 1972 and finished in the top 15 at the Miss World 1972 pageant. Carter is best known as the star of the live-action television series Wonder Woman, in the role of Diana Prince / Wonder Woman.
